---
layout: base.njk
title: Транспорт
description: Хладилен автопарк за контролирани доставки
permalink: /transport/
pagination:
    data: transport
    size: 1000
    alias: fleet
---

<section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="w-full text-left">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#25425E]">Нашият хладилен автопарк</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 text-primary-deepsea max-w-3xl">Изберете подходящото превозно средство според товара, температурния диапазон и дестинацията. Всички камиони и бусове са оборудвани със системи за мониторинг и документиране на студената верига.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-[#25425E]/5 shadow-lg p-4 sm:p-0 sm:bg-transparent sm:shadow-none sm:rounded-none pt-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6 justify-items-center">
                {% for vehicle in fleet %}
                <div class="relative flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-md overflow-hidden w-full max-w-[280px]">
                    <!-- Diagonal Color Block - Absolute to card -->
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full"
                        style="background-color: {{ vehicle.serviceCardColor or '#D8E8DB' }}; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 45%, 0 85%); height: 200px;"
                    ></div>
                    
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full"
                        style="background-color: #4F4F6C; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0 0); height: 200px;"
                    ></div>
                    
                    <!-- Image Container - Full Width, Fixed Height -->
                    <div class="relative h-48 w-full overflow-hidden">
                        <!-- Vehicle Image -->
                        {% if vehicle.images and vehicle.images[0] %}
                            <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex items-center justify-center pt-4">
                                <img
                                    src="{{ vehicle.images[0] | url }}"
                                    alt="{{ vehicle.title }}"
                                    class="w-[80%] max-h-[140px] object-contain"
                                >
                            </div>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Text Content Container - With Padding -->
                    <div class="px-4 py-4 flex flex-col gap-3 flex-1">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-blue leading-snug">
                            {{ vehicle.title }}
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-primary-deepsea leading-relaxed">
                            {{ vehicle.shortDescription or vehicle.short_description }}
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm">
                            {% if vehicle.temperature_range %}
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2 bg-[#25425E]/5 rounded-2xl px-3 py-2">
                                    <span class="font-semibold text-[#25425E]">Температура</span>
                                    <span>{{ vehicle.temperature_range }}</span>
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                            {% if vehicle.capacity %}
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2 bg-[#25425E]/5 rounded-2xl px-3 py-2">
                                    <span class="font-semibold text-[#25425E]">Капацитет</span>
                                    <span>{{ vehicle.capacity }}</span>
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="w-full flex justify-end mt-2">
                            <a
                                href="{{ ('/transport/' ~ vehicle.meta_title ~ '/') | url }}"
                                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary-blue text-white px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200"
                            >
                                Вижте повече
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


